  <description>
    <p>Prey tells the story of Tommy, a Cherokee garage mechanic stuck on a reservation
        going nowhere. Along with his people, he is abducted to a menacing mothership.</p>
    <p>This is a Flatpak distribution of Ryan C. Gordon's Linux port of the game, for
        ease of use as the game can be difficult to run on modern systems.</p>
  </description>
